# Recipe Management System

A simple Python program that allows users to manage and track cooking recipes, including ingredients and difficulty levels.

## Description

This program helps users:
- Create and store multiple recipes
- Track cooking times and ingredients
- Automatically calculate recipe difficulty
- View a sorted list of all ingredients across recipes

## Features

- Recipe input with name, cooking time, and ingredients
- Automatic difficulty calculation based on:
  - Cooking time
  - Number of ingredients
- Display of all recipes with details
- Alphabetically sorted ingredient list
